{"tid":666622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中興翻生？】美議員潑冷水：好可能保留對中興的禁令","createTime":"2018-05-16T04:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T05:40:28.000Z","uid":7369,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bac89eb46e166673e6d0e656ce6a90a27cd46478","tid":666622,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"中美今日起恢復貿易談判，《彭博》引述一位重要的美國共和黨議員表示，美國總統特朗普與中國就中興開拓美國市場能力所達成的任何協議，均不太可能適用於政府機構。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院軍事委員會主席Mac Thornberry表示，不預期美國國會將尋求剔除對中興通訊制裁，又指無論中美可能會達成甚麼協議，眾議院的兩黨議員都希望阻止中興獲得美國不希望中國獲得的信息，並對特朗普早前有意放生中興的言論表示，並不完全理解政府對此的看法，在他看來不是經濟問題，而是安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國參議院情報委員會首席民主黨參議員MarkWarner指，特朗普對中興的舉動似乎是「談判籌碼」，而民主黨參議員Ron Wyden則表示，特朗普的表態引發了非尋常的國家安全問題以及經濟政策擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58198086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198086&d=UFwGXX8V4%2F2YAQ8xCHZgtIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6c2d4958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198086&h=381565ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180516/58198086</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家點睇?</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9af145a36bd5619bd34c763099595836555fa503","tid":666622,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722fe9ff66452cdda973aa08e182fceb879462a2","tid":666622,"uid":57376,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"話左唔係總統一個人話晒事<br />\n而家美國政壇已經普遍對中國有戒心<br />\n個勢開始左就收唔返<br />\n除非中國有本事收買成個商務部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1174b8d05eef0fd5a2ae3f39ca47dd1ce95d613d","tid":6